title: Slider Revolution v4.6.92 - Responsive WordPress Plugin
description:
Create a responsive(mobile friendly) or fullwidth slider with must-see-effects and meanwhile keep or build your SEO optimization (all content always readable for search engines). See the heaps of custom transitions/animations for each object on the page! Customize this slider with our convenient drag&drop backend to your very needs. Contains external links.

To install:

1. Upload to wordpress plugin directory
2. Activate through the plugin section in wp-admin
